or sudden ending of\n2003 outburst in 2005 November was due to a low density region or gap in the\ninner region (~ 1 AU) of the disc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Sep 2013 13:31:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
